@startuml Sequence_Recruiter_Notifications
title Nhà Tuyển Dụng - Quản Lý Thông Báo

actor Recruiter as "👔 Recruiter"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant NotificationService as "Notification\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Danh Sách Thông Báo ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Thông báo"
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: GET /api/notifications?page=0&size=20
NotificationService -> Database: Query thong_bao (recruiterId)
Database --> NotificationService: Return list
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Notifications list
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị danh sách

== Xem Chi Tiết ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click vào thông báo
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: GET /api/notifications/{notificationId}
NotificationService -> Database: Get details
Database --> NotificationService: Full info
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Details
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Xem chi tiết

== Đánh Dấu Đã Xem ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click on notification
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: PATCH /api/notifications/{notificationId}/read
NotificationService -> Database: Update isRead = true
Database --> NotificationService: OK
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Marked as read
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Gray out notification

== Đánh Dấu Tất Cả Đã Xem ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Đánh dấu đã xem tất cả"
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: PATCH /api/notifications/mark-all-read
NotificationService -> Database: Update all isRead = true
Database --> NotificationService: OK
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: All marked
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Tất cả đã xem

== Xem Số Chưa Xem ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: (on header)
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: GET /api/notifications/unread-count
NotificationService -> Database: Count unread
Database --> NotificationService: Count (5)
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Count
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Show badge: 5

== Thông Báo Tự Động ==

note over Recruiter, NotificationService
  Recruiter receives notifications for:
  • Ứng viên nộp đơn mới
  • Cập nhật trạng thái từ candidate
  • Nhắc nhở lịch phỏng vấn
  • Hệ thống thông báo
end note

@enduml
